<subSubSection pageId="85" pageNumber="86" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">
42b. 
<taxonomicName LSID="F91962D5-1055-56C6-8484-9A566F98C2CF" authority="J. R. I. Wood &amp; R. W. Scotland" authorityName="J. R. I. Wood &amp; R. W. Scotland" authorityYear="2015" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Convolvulus equitans subsp. var. var. lindheimeri" order="Solanales" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="equitans" status="var. nov." subSpecies="var." variety="lindheimeri">Convolvulus equitans var. lindheimeri J.R.I.Wood &amp; R.W.Scotland</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel pageId="85" pageNumber="86">var. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="85" pageNumber="86" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">A var, typo floribus grandioribus, sepalis 11 - 12 mm longis, corolla 2.5-3 cm longa, plerumque alba, in centro atropurpurea.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Convolvulus sagittifolius" order="Solanales" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sagittifolius">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Convolvulus sagittifolius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<bibRefCitation author="Scheele, A" journalOrPublisher="Linnaea" pageId="211" pageNumber="212" pagination="747 - 755" refId="B319" refString="Scheele, A, 1849. Beitraege zur Flor von Texas: Convolvulaceae. Linnaea 21: 747 - 755" title="Beitraege zur Flor von Texas: Convolvulaceae." volume="21" year="1849">Scheele (1849</bibRefCitation>
: 747), nom illeg., non 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Convolvulus sagittifolius" order="Solanales" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sagittifolius">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Convolvulus sagittifolius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Michx. (1803).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Type.</emphasis>
Texas, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Neubraunfels”">&quot;Neubraunfels&quot;</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Lindheimer</emphasis>
s.n. (B†).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="85" pageNumber="86" type="type">
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">
UNITED STATES OF AMERICA, Texas, New Braunfels, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">F. Lindheim</emphasis>
er, fasc. IV No. 469 (holotype K; isotypes BM, FHO, LE, P, W).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="85" pageNumber="86" type="distinguishing features">
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Distinguishing features.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Distinguished by it is larger flowers; sepals 11-12 mm long; corolla 2.5-3 cm long, usually white but often with a dark centre.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="85" pageNumber="86" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">
United States, Texas: widely distributed but not common in at least seven Texan counties (
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Lindheimer</emphasis>
fasc. 3: 469, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Siedo</emphasis>
447, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Logan Smith</emphasis>
774, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Hutchins</emphasis>
1035).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="85" pageNumber="86" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="85" pageNumber="86">
Intermediates with 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="subsp. var. var. equitans" order="Solanales" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="sagittifolius" subSpecies="var." variety="equitans">var. equitans</taxonomicName>
occur and 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="subsp. var. var. lindheimeri" order="Solanales" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="sagittifolius" subSpecies="var." variety="lindheimeri">var. lindheimeri</taxonomicName>
may have arisen as a result of hybridisation between 
<taxonomicName authorityName="B. L. Turner, Phytologia 91: 394. 2009. (Turner" authorityYear="2009" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Convolvulus carrii" order="Solanales" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="carrii">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Convolvulus carrii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Benth., Pl. Hartw. 16. 1839. (Bentham" authorityYear="1839" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Convolvulus equitans" order="Solanales" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="equitans">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Convolvulus equitans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
although it is not sympatric with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="B. L. Turner, Phytologia 91: 394. 2009. (Turner" authorityYear="2009" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Convolvulus carrii" order="Solanales" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="carrii">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="85" pageNumber="86">Convolvulus carrii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
